### Station API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5132/api/station

### Get all stations
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get stations by location
GET {{baseUrl}}/location/1

### Get a specific station by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create a station for a location
POST {{baseUrl}}/location/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Salad Bar",
  "description": "Fresh greens and toppings"
}

### Update a station
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deli",
  "description": "Updated deli station description"
}

### Delete a station
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get all business hours for a station
GET {{baseUrl}}/1/hours

### Get specific business hours by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/hours/1

### Add business hours for a station
POST {{baseUrl}}/1/hours
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2025-01-01T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-01-01T17:00:00",
  "weekdayId": 3
}

### Update business hours
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hours/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2025-01-01T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-01-01T18:00:00",
  "weekdayId": 4
}

### Delete business hours
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/hours/1
